CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right,...Karole Russ...Laverne Brown...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Karole Russ wearing light colored satin short sleeve dress with dark tie at waist, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Laverne Brown wearing light colored short sleeve blouse with striped fabric pinned to breast pocket, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
